$ sudo apt update
$ apt-cache policy docker.io # must be > 17
$ sudo apt install docker.io
$ sudo docker pull scrapinghub/splash
$ tmux new -s splash  # quick
$ sudo docker run -it -p 8050:8050 --rm scrapinghub/splash

See:
To SET UA or more params
https://splash.readthedocs.io/en/stable/api.html#arg-headers
https://splash.readthedocs.io/en/stable/api.html#execute-javascript
https://github.com/scrapinghub/splash/issues/628#issuecomment-309606620

